MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping to load data to target table RPT_CLOSEOUT_SELLINGSTYLE
MAPPING.NAME: m_RPT_CLSOT_SELSTY

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Transformation to read data from source
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_CLOSEOUT_INV

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select /*+ ALL_ROWS */ e.cy_year_yyyy, e.cy_month_desc, e.as_of_date, b.facility_id, b.facility_name, a.inventory_type, a.uom, a.dollars, a.garments, round(decode(c.garm_per_pkg_qty,0,0,(a.garments/c.garm_per_pkg_qty))) as Packages, a.stock_category, a.zstyle,flag, c.inv_disposition_route, c.color_code, c.cup_size, c.size_mnemon_code, c.size_code, c.size_desc, c.UPC_Code, decode(a.stock_category,'ZOFQ','I', decode(c.historical_class_code,'-1', decode(c.current_class_code,'1','A','2','I','4','O','6','N','-1'), c.historical_class_code)) as historical_class_code, c.current_class_code, c.style_num, c.color_name, c.pack_code, c.garm_per_pkg_qty,c.inner_box_qty, c.sap_material_num, c.sap_grid_value, c.attribution_code, c.sku, decode(c.division_group,'SLS',c.sku,c.sku_desc) as sku_desc, TRIM(Upper(replace(replace(C.SKU_DESC,'_',''),'-',''))) as trim_sku_desc, d.sbu_desc, d.Style_Group, d.product_group_desc, d.category_desc, d.subcategory_desc, d.Brand_name, d.subbrand_desc, d.silhouette, d.selling_style, d.gender_desc, d.gender_category_desc, d.fabrication, f.oo_dollars as oo_dollars, f.oo_garments as oo_garments, f.oo_packages as oo_packages, g.lifecycle_desc,d.LIFESTYLE_DESC,g.lifecycle_code, d.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC, CASE WHEN row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY decode(c.division_group,'SLS',c.sku,c.sku_desc) order by a.zstyle nulls first,b.facility_id ) =1 Then NVL(sum(f.oo_dollars),0) else 0 end open_orders_Dollars_act, CASE WHEN row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY decode(c.division_group,'SLS',c.sku,c.sku_desc) order by a.zstyle nulls first,b.facility_id ) =1 Then NVL(sum(f.oo_garments),0) else 0 end open_orders_Garments_act, CASE WHEN row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY decode(c.division_group,'SLS',c.sku,c.sku_desc) order by a.zstyle nulls first,b.facility_id ) =1 Then NVL(sum(f.oo_garments),0) else 0 end open_orders_packages_act,
CASE WHEN a.inventory_type='Onhand' then a.dollars else 0 end as Onhand_Dollars, CASE WHEN a.inventory_type='Onhand' then a.garments else 0 end as Onhand_Garments, CASE WHEN a.inventory_type='Onhand' then round(decode(c.garm_per_pkg_qty,0,0,(a.garments/c.garm_per_pkg_qty))) else 0 end as Onhand_Packages,
CASE WHEN a.inventory_type in ('Intransit','Special Stock','Consignment') then a.dollars else 0 end as Intransit_Dollars, CASE WHEN a.inventory_type in ('Intransit','Special Stock','Consignment') then a.garments else 0 end as Intransit_Garments, CASE WHEN a.inventory_type in ('Intransit','Special Stock','Consignment') then round(decode(c.garm_per_pkg_qty,0,0,(a.garments/c.garm_per_pkg_qty))) else 0 end as Intrainsit_Packages, a.PUT_UP_CD
from (select item_id, as_of_date, inventory_type, facility_id, inventory_src, from_facility_id, put_up_cd, stock_category, division_code, dollars, garments, garm_per_pkg_qty, uom, zstyle, flag from staging.STG_CLOSEOUT_INV union all --adjustments select item_id,as_of_date,inventory_type, facility_id, inventory_src, from_facility_id,put_up_cd, stock_category, division_code, dollars, 0 as garments, garm_per_pkg_qty, uom, zstyle, flag from staging.STG_CLOSEOUT_INV_ADJ ) a join (select * from slba.slba_facility where facility_code <> 'IDC' and facility_name not like 'OM-%') b on a.facility_id = b.facility_id join (select * from staging.stg_item_ora ) c on a.item_id = c.item_id left outer join (select * from slba.style_master_1 ) d on c.style_num = d.style_num and c.division_group = upper(d.division_group) and c.company_code = d.company_code join day_dimension e on e.day_date = a.as_of_date left outer join (staging.STG_CLOSEOUT_OO) f on f.item_id = c.item_id left outer join slba.lifecycle_class g on g.lifecycle_code = decode(a.stock_category,'ZOFQ','I', decode(c.historical_class_code,'-1', decode(c.current_class_code,'1','A','2','I', '4','O','6','N','-1'),historical_class_code) ) Where trunc(a.as_of_date) = trunc((SELECT AS_OF_DATE - 7 AS EXPR1 FROM SLBA.DAY_DIMENSION WHERE (TRUNC(DAY_DATE) = TRUNC(SYSDATE))))
Group By e.cy_year_yyyy, e.cy_month_desc, e.as_of_date, b.facility_id, b.facility_name, a.inventory_type, a.uom, a.dollars, a.garments, round(decode(c.garm_per_pkg_qty,0,0,(a.garments/c.garm_per_pkg_qty))), a.stock_category, a.zstyle, flag, c.inv_disposition_route, c.color_code, c.cup_size, c.size_mnemon_code, c.size_code, c.size_desc, c.UPC_Code, decode(a.stock_category,'ZOFQ','I', decode(c.historical_class_code,'-1', decode(c.current_class_code,'1','A','2','I','4','O','6','N','-1'), c.historical_class_code)), c.current_class_code, c.style_num, c.color_name, c.pack_code, c.garm_per_pkg_qty,c.inner_box_qty, c.sap_material_num, c.sap_grid_value, c.attribution_code, c.sku, decode(c.division_group,'SLS',c.sku,c.sku_desc), TRIM(Upper(replace(replace(C.SKU_DESC,'_',''),'-',''))), d.sbu_desc, d.style_Group, d.product_group_desc, d.category_desc, d.subcategory_desc, d.Brand_name, d.subbrand_desc, d.silhouette, d.selling_style, d.gender_desc, d.gender_category_desc, d.fabrication, f.oo_dollars , f.oo_packages , f.oo_garments , g.lifecycle_desc,d.LIFESTYLE_DESC,g.lifecycle_code, d.PRODUCT_LINE_DESC,a.put_up_cd

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_ITEM_SKUDAY.EXEDE_365DAY as EXEDE_365DAY, Upper(stg_item_skuday.SBU) as SBU, Upper(stg_item_skuday.Color_Desc) as COLOR_DESC, TRIM(Upper(replace(replace(stg_item_skuday.SKU,'_',''),'-',''))) as SKU_DESC ,Upper(stg_item_skuday.SIZE_DESC) as SIZE_DESC FROM STG_ITEM_SKUDAY STG_ITEM_SKUDAY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SBU = I_SBU AND COLOR_DESC = I_COLOR_CODE AND SKU_DESC = I_SKU_DESC AND SIZE_DESC = I_SIZE_DESC
